T1  - LAST BUT NOT LEAST: LAGGARD FIRMS, TECHNOLOGY DIFFUSION, AND ITS STRUCTURAL AND POLICY DETERMINANTS
AU  - Berlingieri, Giuseppe
AU  - Calligaris, Sara
AU  - Criscuolo, Chiara
AU  - Verlhac, Rudy
